1649-1655 Victory Boulevard, at the N.E. corner of
Hodges Place (at the head of Todt Hill Road), showing the Castleton Hill Moravian Church. In 1898 it was known as the Moravian Collegiate Church, and in 1907 as the United Brethen Church.

April, 1930
P. L. Sperr
